《'''打得火熱'''》（{{lang-en|"Hotter than Hell"}}）是[[英國|英國]]歌手[[杜娃·黎波|杜娃·黎波]]演唱的一首歌曲，出自其{{tsl|en|Dua Lipa (album)|杜娃·黎波 (專輯)|首張同名專輯}}。這首歌曲由黎波和{{tsl|en|Ritual (electronic band)|Ritual (樂團)|Ritual}}成員亞當·米德利、湯米·巴克斯特和杰拉德·奧康奈爾負責創作，而{{tsl|en|Stephen Kozmeniuk|斯蒂芬·科玆梅紐克|斯蒂芬·「科玆」·科玆梅紐克}}則負責製作。它作為專輯第4支單曲於2016年5月6日由杜娃·黎波有限公司以[[數位音樂下載|數位下載]]和[[流媒體|串流]]形式發行。《打得火熱》跨越多種音樂類型，包括[[流行舞曲|流行舞曲]]、[[迪斯科|迪斯科]]、[[電子舞曲|電子舞曲]]、[[電子流行|電子流行]]、[[当代节奏布鲁斯|R&B]][[House_(音樂)|浩室]]和[[热带浩室|热带浩室]]，並參雜了{{tsl|en|dancehall|舞廳 (音樂)|舞廳}}元素。歌曲圍繞對無法忘記她的前男友進行嘲諷。

《打得火熱》獲得廣泛好評，大多數讚賞它{{tsl|en|tropical music|熱帶音樂|熱帶}}曲調。它成為黎波第一首進入[[英國單曲排行榜|英國單曲排行榜]]的歌曲，並最高到達第15位。歌曲在比利時、荷蘭、波蘭和斯洛文尼亞的榜單取得前40位的成績。《打得火熱》受[[澳大利亚唱片业协会|澳大利亚唱片业协会]]和[[英国唱片业协会|英国唱片业协会]]分別[[音乐唱片销售认证|認證]]為金唱片和白金唱片。

《打得火熱》的隨行[[音樂錄影帶|音樂錄影帶]]由{{tsl|en|Emil Nava|埃米爾·納瓦}}執導。影片拍攝於[[倫敦|倫敦]]的倉庫，它在視覺上呈現了一場夜晚派對，當中囊括了數個背景、燈光和一顆迪斯科球。黎波在《[[吉米·法伦今夜秀|吉米·法伦今夜秀]]》、《{{tsl|en|RTL Late Night|RTL深夜秀}}》和《{{tsl|en|Sommarkrysset}}》演唱該曲以作宣傳。

==背景與發行==
2013年，黎波與一些管理層公司開會時遇見了Tap的管理層本·莫森（{{lang|en|Ben Mawson}}）和埃德·米利特（{{lang|en|Ed Millett}}）。莫森和米利特賞識到她的天賦後為她開設創作課程，並完成《打得火熱》<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.musicbusinessworldwide.com/artists-have-the-best-chance-of-success-when-they-get-things-rolling-themselves/|title=Artists Have the Best Chance of Success When They Get Things Rolling Themselves|website=Music Business Worldwide|date=2018-06-22|accessdate=2020-07-08|last=Jones|first=Rhian|dead-url=no|archive-url=https://archive.today/20200708190915/https://www.musicbusinessworldwide.com/artists-have-the-best-chance-of-success-when-they-get-things-rolling-themselves/|archive-date=2020-07-08}}</ref>。歌曲由黎波與英國[[電子音樂|電子]]樂團{{tsl|en|Ritual (electronic band)|Ritual (樂團)|Ritual}}成員亞當·米德利（{{lang|en|Adam Midgley}}）、湯米·巴克斯特（{{lang|en|Tommy Baxter}}）和杰拉德·奧康奈爾（{{lang|en|Gerard O'Connell}}）共同創作，而{{tsl|en|Stephen Kozmeniuk|斯蒂芬·科玆梅紐克}}、{{tsl|en|Jay Reynolds (producer)|傑伊·雷諾茲}}和湯姆·內維爾（{{lang|en|Tom Neville}}）分別負責製作、額外製作和聲樂製作<ref name = "Notes"/>。歌曲以[[键盘_(音乐)|鍵盤]]和[[大鼓|踢鼓]]開始，而沒有任何其他音樂參雜其中<ref name = "Attitude">{{cite web|url=https://attitude.co.uk/article/interview-dua-lipa-talks-dark-pop-gay-fans-and-her-secret-weapon/10351/|title=Interview Dua Lipa Talks Dark Pop, Gay Fans, and Her 'Secret Weapon'|website=[[態度_(雜誌)|Attitude]]|date=2016-06-05|accessdate=2020-07-08|dead-url=no|archive-url=https://archive.today/20200625170218/https://attitude.co.uk/article/interview-dua-lipa-talks-dark-pop-gay-fans-and-her-secret-weapon/10351/|archive-date=2020-06-25}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.standard.co.uk/lifestyle/esmagazine/dua-lipa-meet-pops-hottest-property-a3672811.html|title=Dua Lipa: meet pop's hottest property|work=Evening Standard|date=2017-11-01|accessdate=2020-07-08|dead-url=no|archive-url=https://archive.today/20200708192106/https://www.standard.co.uk/lifestyle/esmagazine/dua-lipa-meet-pops-hottest-property-a3672811.html|archive-date=2020-07-08}}</ref>。黎波啟發自一段戀情，當時男友讓她覺得自己不夠好<ref name = "NME">{{cite web|url=https://www.nme.com/news/music/dua-lipa-ex-boyfriend-manipulative-inspiration-hotter-than-hell-lyrics-meaning-2249450|title=Dua Lipa discusses inspiration from 'terrible' and 'manipulative' ex-boyfriends|website=[[新音乐快递|NME]]|date=2018-02-27|accessdate=2020-07-08|last=Trendell|first=Andrew|dead-url=no|archive-url=https://archive.today/20200708193046/https://www.nme.com/news/music/dua-lipa-ex-boyfriend-manipulative-inspiration-hotter-than-hell-lyrics-meaning-2249450|archive-date=2020-07-08}}</ref>。黎波原先因為想不出副歌部分，所以打算不要這首歌。然而，她開始瀏覽[[Tumblr|Tumblr]]時看到用紅色寫在黑色背景的「Hotter than Hell」。她接著想「如果他認為我比地獄更火辣，但我卻（對他）毫無掛念？」<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.rollingstone.com/music/music-features/dua-lipa-pops-warrior-of-love-202696/|title=Dua Lipa: 'New Rules' Singer Talks Bad Exes, Max Martin|work=[[滾石_(雜誌)|Rolling Stone]]|date=2018-02-23|accessdate=2020-07-08|last=Weiner|first=Jonah|dead-url=no|archive-url=https://archive.today/20200708193039/https://www.rollingstone.com/music/music-features/dua-lipa-pops-warrior-of-love-202696/|archive-date=2020-07-08}}</ref>合作人之後改了歌曲意思，似乎改讓黎波佔上風，而男友反而無法滿足她<ref name = "NME"/><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.dailytelegraph.com.au/entertainment/sydney-confidential/dua-lipa-has-no-regrets-for-giving-up-modelling-to-concentrate-on-music/news-story/7b438488655d092357ddd0cbf6886728|title=Dua Lipa has no regrets for giving up modelling to concentrate on music|website=[[每日电讯报_(澳洲)|The Daily Telegraph (Sydney)]]|last=Moran|first=Jonathon|date=2016-07-15|accessdate=2020-07-08|dead-url=no|archive-url=https://archive.today/20160928170544/http://www.dailytelegraph.com.au/entertainment/sydney-confidential/dua-lipa-has-no-regrets-for-giving-up-modelling-to-concentrate-on-music/news-story/7b438488655d092357ddd0cbf6886728|archive-date=2016-09-28}}</ref>。黎波認為創作這首歌對她來說「非常有療癒作用」<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.digitalspy.com/music/new-music/a776876/meet-your-new-favourite-popstar-dua-lipa-just-dont-call-her-the-new-lana-del-rey/|title=Meet your new favourite popstar Dua Lipa - just don't call her the new Lana Del Rey|website=[[數碼間諜|Digital Spy]]|date=2015-12-11|accessdate=2020-07-08|last=Davidson|first=Amy|dead-url=no|archive-url=https://archive.today/20200708194739/https://www.digitalspy.com/music/new-music/a776876/meet-your-new-favourite-popstar-dua-lipa-just-dont-call-her-the-new-lana-del-rey/|archive-date=2020-07-08}}</ref>。

《打得火熱》是首批在黎波2017年的首張同名專輯創作的歌曲。它奠定了專輯其他歌曲的風格，並讓她察覺到自身音樂風格是屬於{{tsl|en|Darkness in music|黑暗中的音樂|黑暗流行}}類型<ref name = "Complex">{{cite web|url=https://www.complex.com/music/2016/08/interview-dua-lipa|title=Meet Dua Lipa, The London Singer Whose Pop Is Hotter Than Hell|work=Complex|date=2016-08-10|accessdate=2020-07-08|last=Mooro|first=Alya|dead-url=no|archive-url=https://archive.today/20200708213351/https://www.complex.com/music/2016/08/interview-dua-lipa|archive-date=2020-07-08}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=imYY_-8y7VE|title=How I Wrote That Song: Dua Lipa 'Hotter Than Hell'|via=[[YouTube|YouTube]]|date=2016-08-03|author=[[吉米·法伦今夜秀|The Tonight Show Starring Jimmy Fallon]]|accessdate=2020-07-08|archive-url=https://archive.today/20200708213859/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=imYY_-8y7VE|archive-date=2020-07-08|dead-url=no}}</ref>。[[華納音樂集團|華納音樂]]於2015年聽了這首歌後便與黎波簽下{{tsl|en|recording contract|唱片合同}}<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/pop/7709315/dua-lipa-rejecting-modeling-trove-sivan-strip-club|title='Dark Pop' Purveyor Dua Lipa on Rejecting Modeling & Hitting the Strip Club With Troye Sivan|website=[[告示牌_(雜誌)|Billboard]]|date=2017-03-02|accessdate=2020-07-08|last=Adams|first=William Lee|dead-url=no|archive-url=https://archive.today/20200708214859/https://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/pop/7709315/dua-lipa-rejecting-modeling-trove-sivan-strip-club|archive-date=2020-07-08}}</ref>。2016年2月，黎波接受[[英国广播公司|BBC]]訪問時首次透露歌曲將會作為《杜娃·黎波》的第4支單曲<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.bbc.com/news/entertainment-arts-35520865|title=Dua Lipa: A pop star in waiting|publisher=[[英国广播公司|BBC]]|date=2016-02-09|accessdate=2020-07-08|last=Savage|first=Mark|dead-url=no|archive-url=https://archive.today/20160306102218/http://www.bbc.com/news/entertainment-arts-35520865|archive-date=2016-03-06}}</ref>。《打得火熱》於2016年5月6日由黎波的[[獨立唱片公司|獨立唱片公司]]杜娃·黎波有限公司（{{lang|en|Dua Lipa Limited}}）以[[數位音樂下載|數位下載]]和[[流媒體|串流]]形式發行<ref name="iTunes"/>。它在英國和義大利以[[當代流行電台|當代流行電台]]形式發行<ref name = "ukradio"/><ref name = "italyradio"/>。它之後收錄在黎波於2017年6月2日發行的首張同名專輯的第3首歌曲<ref name = "Notes"/>。歌曲有包括{{tsl|en|Miike Snow|麥克史諾樂團}}和{{tsl|en|Matoma|馬托馬}}的幾首重混。麥克史諾樂團的重混歌曲將節奏放慢、扭曲旋律並加入[[迪斯科|迪斯科]][[Groove_(音樂)|動感]]<ref name = "complex miike snow">{{cite web|url=https://www.complex.com/music/2016/06/dua-lipa-hotter-than-hell-miike-snow-remix-premiere|title=Premiere: Get Down to Miike Snow's Dance-Ready Remix of Dua Lipa's 'Hotter Than Hell'|work=Complex|date=2016-06-02|accessdate=2020-07-08|last=Ortiz|first=Edwin|dead-url=no|archive-url=https://archive.today/20200708222247/https://www.complex.com/music/2016/06/dua-lipa-hotter-than-hell-miike-snow-remix-premiere|archive-date=2020-07-08}}</ref><ref name = "BillboardRemixes">{{cite web|url=https://www.billboard.com/articles/news/dance/8038283/dua-lipa-songs-best-remixes-list|title=The 10 Best Dua Lipa Remixes: Critic's Picks|website=Billboard|date=2017-11-11|accessdate=2020-07-08|last=Bein|first=Kat|dead-url=no|archive-url=https://archive.today/20200708222257/https://www.billboard.com/articles/news/dance/8038283/dua-lipa-songs-best-remixes-list|archive-date=2020-07-08}}</ref>。黎波稱重混「讓（她）想起來跳舞」，而{{tsl|en|Complex Networks|Complex網站|Complex}}的埃德溫·奧爾蒂斯（{{lang|en|Edwin Ortiz}}）稱它是「同樣令人滿足的表演，將原作從夜店轉移至城市的天台派對」<ref name = "complex miike snow"/>。《[[告示牌_(雜誌)|告示牌]]》的吉·貝因（{{lang|en|Kat Bein}}）認為馬托馬的重混是「在烈日下的海灘和開著敞篷車的長途車程（會播放）」<ref name = "BillboardRemixes"/>。

