==商業表現==
《打得火熱》在歐洲和大洋洲稍微取得成功。它是黎波首次進入[[英國單曲排行榜|英國單曲排行榜]]的歌曲，並於2016年5月13日空降第50位<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.officialcharts.com/charts/singles-chart/20160513/7501/|title=Official Singles Chart Top 100|publisher=[[官方榜单公司|Official Charts Company]]|date=2016-05-13|accessdate=2020-07-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190327143349/https://www.officialcharts.com/charts/singles-chart/20160513/7501/|archive-date=2019-03-27|dead-url=no}}</ref>。歌曲於2016年7月1日升上第15位，並持續3週<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.officialcharts.com/charts/singles-chart/20160701/7501/|title=Official Singles Chart Top 100|publisher=Official Charts Company|date=2016-07-01|accessdate=2020-07-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200709003428/https://www.officialcharts.com/charts/singles-chart/20160701/7501/|archive-date=2020-07-09|dead-url=no}}</ref>。它總共呆在榜單21週<ref name = "UK"/>。它連續4週在[[BBC廣播一台|BBC廣播一台]]是最多次播放的歌曲，並在英國商業電台達到最大的升幅<ref>{{cite web|url=https://press.warnerrecords.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/dua-lipa-global-press-kit_1481573911262.pdf|publisher=[[华纳唱片|Warner Records]]|title=Dua Lipa - Global Press Kit|accessdate=2020-07-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200709101300/https://press.warnerrecords.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/dua-lipa-global-press-kit_1481573911262.pdf|archive-date=2020-07-09|dead-url=no}}</ref>。《打得火熱》接著在澳洲、愛爾蘭和蘇格蘭的榜單最高排在前40位<ref name = "IRE"/><ref name = "SCO"/>。它獲得幾項[[音乐唱片销售认证|銷量認證]]，分別受[[英國唱片業協會|英國唱片業協會]]和[[澳大利亚唱片业协会|澳大利亚唱片业协会]]認證為白金唱片和金唱片<ref name = "UK cert"/><ref name = "AUS cert"/>。

==音樂錄影帶==
===背景與反嚮===
《打得火熱》的[[音樂錄影帶|音樂錄影帶]]於2016年5月6日在黎波的[[YouTube|YouTube]]頻道首映<ref name = "YT">{{cite web|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=fEOyePhElr4|title=Dua Lipa - Hotter Than Hell (Official Video)|via=YouTube|date=2016-05-06|accessdate=2020-07-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200620165800/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=fEOyePhElr4|archive-date=2020-06-20|dead-url=no}}</ref>。它由{{tsl|en|Emil Nava|埃米爾·納瓦}}執導，並在[[倫敦|倫敦]]的倉庫拍攝<ref name = "RSMV">{{cite web|url=https://www.rollingstone.com/music/music-news/watch-dua-lipas-steamy-hotter-than-hell-video-87219/|title=Watch Dua Lipa's Steamy 'Hotter Than Hell' Video|work=Rolling Stone|date=2016-05-06|accessdate=2020-07-11|last=Spanos|first=Brittany|dead-url=no|archive-url=https://archive.today/20160828133256/http://www.rollingstone.com/music/news/watch-dua-lipas-steamy-hotter-than-hell-video-20160506|archive-date=2016-08-28}}</ref>。黎波在影片中打算展示她對地獄的想法，就是倫敦的陰暗面以及表達她家鄉的「迷途羔羊」<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.gq.com/story/wcw-dua-lipa|title=Meet British Singer Dua Lipa, Who Just Fell Hard for American Crowds|work=[[GQ|GQ]]|date=2016-05-18|accessdate=2020-07-11|last=Lange|first=Maggie|dead-url=no|archive-url=https://archive.today/20200711040419/https://www.gq.com/story/wcw-dua-lipa|archive-date=2020-07-11}}</ref>。部分的影評用[[超8毫米胶片|超8毫米胶片]]拍攝<ref name = "Promonews"/>。《滾石》的布蘭妮·斯帕諾斯（{{lang|en|Brittany Spanos}}）稱背景「美麗動人」，而《{{tsl|en|V (American magazine)|V (美國雜誌)|V}}》的萊拉·伊爾奇（{{lang|en|Layla Ilchi}}）稱燈光「色彩繽紛」和「有迷幻效果」<ref name = "RSMV"/><ref>{{cite web|url=https://vmagazine.com/article/dua-lipa-is-hotter-than-hell/|title=Dua Lipa Is Hotter Than Hell|work=V|date=2016-05-06|accessdate=2020-07-11|last=Ilchi|first=Layla|dead-url=no|archive-url=https://archive.today/20200711042057/https://vmagazine.com/article/dua-lipa-is-hotter-than-hell/|archive-date=2020-07-11}}</ref>。《{{tsl|en|DIY (magazine)|DIY (雜誌)|DIY}}》稱影片完全如「夢境」<ref>{{cite web|url=https://diymag.com/2016/05/06/dua-lipa-hotter-than-hell-single|title=Dua Lipa's new 'Hotter Than Hell' single is huge|work=DIY|date=2016-05-06|accessdate=2020-07-11|dead-url=no|archive-url=https://archive.today/20200711042253/https://diymag.com/2016/05/06/dua-lipa-hotter-than-hell-single|archive-date=2020-07-11}}</ref>。

