===概要===
[[File:Dua_Lipa_-_Hotter_than_Hell_video_screenshot.png|thumb]]中，杜娃·黎波坐在派對的寶座中，身邊圍繞著同行的派對常客<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.universal-music.de/dua-lipa/videos/hotter-than-hell-400554|title=Dua Lipa - Video - Hotter Than Hell|publisher=[[环球音乐集团|Universal Music Germany]]|accessdate=2020-07-11|dead-url=no|archive-url=https://archive.today/20200711153608/https://www.universal-music.de/dua-lipa/videos/hotter-than-hell-400554|archive-date=2020-07-11}}</ref>。]]

影片的背景位於倉庫，當中正在舉辦了黑暗又性感的秘密派對<ref name = "Promonews"/>。一群派對常客坐在沙發和地上，中間有一部放在架子上的電視。黎波走進紅光中，一位派對常客坐在椅子上拍攝對面的人，之後黎波將手放在磚牆上。黎波將迪斯科球放在大腿上滾動，並轉為掛著迪斯科球的黑暗房間，之後她站在畫了雨林的牆壁前。黎波接著坐在紅色的寶座，身邊圍繞著同行的派對常客。她還站在房間的中間，並在充滿藍光的房間中甩頭髮，之後在帶有投影的磚牆前跳舞和在洋紅色的背景前唱歌。派對常客在整部影片中放鬆、拍攝、刺青、在其他人身上灑滿金粉和跳舞<ref>{{cite web|url=https://iwantmypopculture.com/2017/11/20/video-review-dua-lipa-hotter-than-hell/|title=Video Review: Dua Lipa 'Hotter Than Hell'|work=I Want My Pop Culture|last=Avoledo|first=Pam|date=2017-11-20|accessdate=2020-07-11|dead-url=no|archive-url=https://archive.today/20200711045300/https://iwantmypopculture.com/2017/11/20/video-review-dua-lipa-hotter-than-hell/|archive-date=2020-07-11}}</ref>。在影片當中派對常客有一度在拍攝躺在床墊上的黎波<ref name = "YT"/>。

==現場演出==
《打得火熱》包含在{{tsl|en|List of Dua Lipa concert tours#Hotter Than Hell Tour (2016)|杜娃·黎波巡迴演唱會列表|打得火熱巡迴演唱會}}和{{tsl|en|List of Dua Lipa concert tours#The Self-Titled Tour (2017–2018)|杜娃·黎波巡迴演唱會列表|同名巡迴演唱會}}的曲目列表中<ref>{{cite web|url=https://celebmix.com/dua-lipa-hotter-than-hell-tour/|title=Review: Dua Lipa's mind-blowing Hotter Than Hell Tour|publisher=CelebMix|date=2016-10-10|accessdate=2020-07-11|last=Willis|first=Mark|dead-url=no|archive-url=https://archive.today/20200627131909/https://celebmix.com/dua-lipa-hotter-than-hell-tour/|archive-date=2020-06-27}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.theguardian.com/music/2018/apr/13/dua-lipa-review-pop-hydro-glasgow|title=Dua Lipa review – bouncing, ballads and full-bore pop bangers|website=[[衛報|The Guardian]]|date=2018-04-13|accessdate=2020-07-11|last=Virtue|first=Graeme|dead-url=no|archive-url=https://archive.today/20200627131903/https://www.theguardian.com/music/2018/apr/13/dua-lipa-review-pop-hydro-glasgow|archive-date=2020-06-27}}</ref>。黎波於2016年6月2日在荷蘭深夜脫口秀《{{tsl|en|RTL Late Night|RTL深夜秀}}》演出<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.rtllatenight.nl/item/2557/dua_lipa_hotter_than_hell/ |title=Dua Lipa – Hotter Than Hell |work=RTL Late Night |accessdate=2016-08-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161022054732/http://www.rtllatenight.nl/item/2557/dua_lipa_hotter_than_hell/ |archive-date=2016-10-22 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。7月9日，她在德國遊戲節目《{{tsl|en|Beat the Star|Schlag den Star}}》演唱歌曲<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.prosieben.de/tv/schlag-den-star/video/83-saengerin-dua-lipa-ein-heisser-britisch-albanischer-export-clip |title=Sängerin Dua Lipa – ein heißer britisch-albanischer Export |trans-title=Singer Dua Lipa – a hot British-Albanian export |publisher=ProSieben |date=2016-07-09 |accessdate=2016-08-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160711081444/http://www.prosieben.de/tv/schlag-den-star/video/83-saengerin-dua-lipa-ein-heisser-britisch-albanischer-export-clip |archive-date=2016-07-11 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。黎波於8月2日《[[吉米·法伦今夜秀|吉米·法伦今夜秀]]》演唱歌曲，為她美國電視首秀<ref name = "Spin"/>。她身後跟著鼓手和兩名鍵盤手，並穿著黑色網狀衣和高筒靴<ref name = "RS Jimmy"/><ref name = "Idolator Jimmy">{{cite web|url=https://www.idolator.com/7641943/dua-lipa-hotter-than-hell-tonight-show?chrome=1|title=Watch Dua Lipa’s Sultry Performance Of 'Hotter Than Hell' On 'Fallon'|publisher=Idolator|last=Sonis|first=Rachel|date=2016-08-03|accessdate=2020-07-11|dead-url=no|archive-url=https://archive.today/20200711143403/https://www.idolator.com/7641943/dua-lipa-hotter-than-hell-tonight-show?chrome=1|archive-date=2020-07-11}}</ref>。索尼斯稱演出「受到抑制」，而《V》的加布里埃拉·薩爾金（{{lang|en|Gabriella Salkin}}）稱它「傑出」<ref name = "Idolator Jimmy"/><ref>{{cite web|url=https://vmagazine.com/article/dua-lipa-kills-tonight-show-announces-new-album-details/|title=Dua Lipa Kills It On 'The Tonight Show,' Announces New Album Details|work=V|last=Salkin|first=Gabriella|date=2016-08-03|accessdate=2020-07-11|dead-url=no|archive-url=https://archive.today/20170605015408/http://vmagazine.com/article/dua-lipa-kills-tonight-show-announces-new-album-details/|archive-date=2017-06-05}}</ref>。她還於2016年8月13日在瑞典節目《{{tsl|en|Sommarkrysset|Sommarkrysset}}》演唱《打得火熱》<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.tv4.se/sommarkrysset/klipp/dua-lipa-hotter-than-hell-3472650 |title=Dua Lipa – Hotter Than Hell |work=Sommarkrysset |date=2016-08-13 |accessdate=2016-10-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190922080008/https://www.tv4.se/sommarkrysset/klipp/dua-lipa-hotter-than-hell-3472650 |archive-date=2019-09-22 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。歌曲還包括在黎波於2016年11月20日在[[紐約|紐約]]{{tsl|en|Iridium Jazz Club|Iridium爵士酒吧|Iridium}}的[[音樂電視網|MTV]]演出曲目中<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.popmatters.com/dua-lipa-mtv-setlist-preview-2495407837.html|title=Dua Lipa Records MTV 'Setlist' Performance for Small, Rapturous Audience (Photos)|work=[[PopMatters|PopMatters]]|last=Mital|first=Sachyn|date=2016-11-21|accessdate=2020-07-11|dead-url=no|archive-url=https://archive.today/20200711143420/https://www.popmatters.com/dua-lipa-mtv-setlist-preview